author: Unreal Engine
description:
Twinmotion is being leveraged in the automotive industry more and more to explore early concepts in design reviews, market finished vehicles, and convey technical details for after-sales services.

In this session, we take a dive into some of the use cases of Twinmotion for auto designers, highlighting the new tools that have been added in Twinmotion 2025.1. 

You’ll get a look at the Twinmotion tools that turn raw automotive 3D models into compelling Twinmotion presentations which can help wow clients and sell ideas faster. 

Come by and learn how to stage vehicles, animate scenes, and add the polish that makes your work stand out in pitches, reels, and social content.
title: Shifting Gears: The Power of Twinmotion for Automotive Design | Unreal Fest Orlando 2025
